                        {
                            "key": "XT-29889",
                            "title": "Reordering - Rules per item/site",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-29889\" target=\"_blank\">XT-29889</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>A stock managed item must now be Purchased and/or Manufactured, and the Item-site's Replenishment rules have been simplified:</p><ul><li>The Preferred process is now dependent on item type</li><li>The Batch quantity applies to both Purchasing and Production</li><li>Economic order quantity has been added</li><li>Average daily consumption has been removed</li></ul><p>\u00a0</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
