                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>The purchase invoice page now has a \"Create credit memo\" button. It enables the user to create a credit memo document directly from the purchase invoice.</p><p>For the credit memo creation to be done, there is mandatory information to be filled out in a dialog box (Reason, Supplier document date, and Total amount). \u00a0</p>",
