                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>Item-sites are <em>locked</em> i.e. stock can be neither receipted nor issued through the stock service, when a Stock count including stock belonging to those item-sites is started. The locks are removed once the Stock count is completed or the stock detail is excluded from the Stock count.</p>",
